```python id=golden
import numpy as np
# controlled-R4 (control=first, big-endian): diag(1,1,1, exp(2*pi*i/2**4))
golden = np.diag([1, 1, 1, np.exp(2j*np.pi/2**4)]).astype(complex)
```
